      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained luxury sedan that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The exterior boasts a deep metallic luster, though it shows minor signs of careful use such as a few light stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is in excellent shape with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, and the dual-zone climate control and infotainment systems work flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, refined ride. This is an ideal opportunity for a buyer seeking a premium, reliable vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of enjoyment.",
